{"tid":814674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔小心格式化左老細d文件","createTime":"2018-09-11T11:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T12:48:42.000Z","uid":82670,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"92e0bd46198c52bc87c878292c1962c536801f72","tid":814674,"uid":82670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"話說今日老細比左個hard disk比我<br />\n咁佢平時用開windows我用mac<br />\n咁我手快快咁唔知禁左咩就拉左去d野去佢個file<br />\n最後佢入面d野唔見晒...得返我比佢d野...<br />\n我估就係我格式化左佢d文件<br />\n咁我咁岩係大陸就拎左上華強北整...<br />\n點知佢都係話整唔返全部文件<br />\n原因以下<br />\n一，個hard disk本身有d損壞所以開唔到<br />\n二，我格式化左仲要放左野落去<br />\n依加最重要果幾樣都冇左<br />\n我係咪準備要汁包袱走<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90820252793dbd1ddccb019e6633089831c0a2f","tid":814674,"uid":112393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e60a9ab2722c87b97b958fd8cfd7af21d59684","tid":814674,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acad6eff1b48720310194e21586b362f724e5ae6","tid":814674,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2250c862e9220e1fe62250158ecf566d69af4a28","tid":814674,"uid":52727,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:50:39.000Z","msg":"同你老細講隻硬碟壞咗"},{"pid":"872c1985578f45993c62f196ddbfb6a74f2979e8","tid":814674,"uid":175683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7809c1210624656e8a7f43da75b65cbcec6600a5","tid":814674,"uid":33939,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11