 file比病毒delete咗。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:03:42.000Z","msg":"屌老細已經覺得係我整壞🙈<br />\n屈返佢都冇咩意思<br />\n依加hdd已經還返比佢...<br />\n但大陸果邊公司就話一係再比佢地深度整多次..睇下救唔救得返<br />\n但我已經唔敢再問老細再拎黎搞<br />\n到時又搞唔到又賴我多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉....好灰....<br />\n做左成年話晒我都盡晒力幫公司賺錢...<br />\n件事真係我有問題<br />\n聽日準備汁包服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0013bc76fd5393bbab2e745550e8ecf49e8eab","tid":814674,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:07:12.000Z","msg":"嗱嗱聲執<br />\n執多一秒佢屌多你一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主下世小心啲"},{"pid":"79ef17cdaa31dd04b0dd550fe3c20971c761aef7","tid":814674,"uid":82670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:11:29.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n個維修人員都話原本個hdd都係有問題<br />\n我肯定我係禁back up文件既...<br />\n但依加結果就係唔見晒d野<br />\n但我真係覺得係我責任做錯左<br />\n真係好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算老細原諒左我<br />\n我都覺得我已經唔可以原諒<br />\n我個心都好唔舒服<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b2867c45923dc14339826b0a5399f4e0913a46","tid":814674,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:32:57.000Z","msg":"下次小心D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1ca0846d5820f7c4b577ff0218d9378988c356","tid":814674,"uid":82670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"有冇電腦高手可以答下我，<br />\n係咪唔同人唔同既技術會對拎返d文件有影響，<br />\n我搵第二個人整會唔會有大d機會拎返d文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似做手術咁"},{"pid":"8b24919e22b536f676c630022e1b62a96ea0de09","tid":814674,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b1ca0846d5820f7c4b577ff0218d9378988c356","tid":814674,"uid":